arn.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the security group rule.

fromPort.description: The start of port range for the TCP and UDP protocols, or an ICMP/ICMPv6 type.

ipProtocol.description: The IP protocol name or number. Use `-1` to specify all protocols. Note that if `ip_protocol` is set to `-1`, it translates to all protocols, all port ranges, and `from_port` and `to_port` values should not be defined.

prefixListId.description: The ID of the source prefix list.

securityGroupId.description: The ID of the security group.

securityGroupRuleId.description: The ID of the security group rule.
